{"tid":220602,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"最近發現左男朋友成日用我個連登ac扮女人","createTime":"2017-04-28T05:30:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-28T11:49:24.000Z","uid":68626,"like":29,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"599137bc3b8f14bb30d6a7ccfcb175cdfc82eae3","tid":220602,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T05:30:22.000Z","msg":"本身我都冇乜點睇返自己開過咩post既<br />\n點知今日係個莊group度有個男同學share左連登個post出黎<br />\n屌鳩個樓主臭閪公廁 <br />\n正當我打算留言屌鳩埋個樓主一份既時候<br />\n發現個ac名咁撚熟口面既<br />\n屌奶星 原來係我自己個ac<br />\n應該係我男朋友出post<br />\n仲成日小妹前小妹後好撚噁心<br />\n之後我問佢係咪用我ac扮女人<br />\n佢又話咩我地二位一體邊有男女之分...<br />\n雖然我覺得佢有時扮女人詭辯屌連登仔都幾man...<br />\n但係我真係接受唔倒自己男朋友咁變態<br />\n開咁多呢d po 我應唔應該同佢分手<br />\n分:正皮<br />\n唔分:負皮"},{"pid":"0510fb8309f22e750fdafc6a9ec210f3b1897377","tid":220602,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T05:33:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c77b4add930c8523c4c02bdb3ab7067d89f9bf56","tid":220602,"uid":72816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T05:37:47.000Z","msg":"扮咩啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a2763abfc31013d41c66647cd68b2cb7470ba52","tid":220602,"uid":110719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T05:38:57.000Z","msg":"第2人格出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"384ca124a1c156b8a2e529d20ab7ff1ce8b84c68","tid":220602,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T05:40:25.000Z","msg":"佢話以後都唔敢<br />\n比唔比個機會佢好？"},{"pid":"15cc41b50ca4f733e3d0fd25881ba8f000cb97d9","tid":220602,"uid":17322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T05:42:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3b0182fd28873488bfec6ae5539042c653c1bc93","tid":220602,"uid":26110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T05:43:05.000Z","msg":"思覺失調<br />\n未係好嚴重<br />\n快d 去睇醫生"},{"pid":"4faa02526